high_descs: Go straight, turn right and walk, turn left and walk across the sofa, then turn right and walk towards the tv stand.
Pick up the watch from the tv stand.
Turn right and walk, again turn right and walk towards the side table beside the sofa.
Put the watch into the mug back side of the bowl on the side table.
Pick up the mug along with watch from the side table.
Put the mug with watch inside in the down shelf of the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug along with watch in the down shelf of the side table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the TV stand.
Take the watch from the TV stand.
Turn around and go near the mug.
Put the watch into the cup.
Then take the cup with watch from the table.
Put the cup with watch on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cup with watch on the shelf.

high_descs: Head towards to the tv stand
Take a watch with the mug
Keep the mug into the shelf
anns.task_desc: Keep the mug into the shelf
